title: Motor City Motors
overview: A city that has seen it fortunes rise and fall, now has its close-up. Detroit is ready to show the world that its still got muscle in Motor City Motors. As founders of Detroit Bros. Custom Cycles, Dave and Jamie Kaye are renowned fabricators and imaginative builders. With dad John, the brothers tap into other Detroit-based talent to assemble builders and specialists to push the boundaries of automotive engineering and create one-of-a-kind vehicles.
